      "width": 460,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Modularization Boundaries\n\nTwilite now needs replaceable subsystem seams, not just smaller files. This graph defines the modules that should be swappable and the contracts they need between them.",
